的link入去</span></strong></span>，又或者YouTube channel<br />\n<br />\n但廢J我完全不識點樣整呢D片出來，卡通又好真人又好，都唔識，眾籌也沒experience。所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想集結神力，有邊位兄弟覺得有得諗，就幫手spread出去同用力push，小弟廢J P牌仔自push都做唔到</span></span></strong>，sosaad。"},{"pid":"8b6aa604388eafe3ad5d95754384e763920009be","tid":1577170,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cf94cf940e4b58333ece64a515a1c9a85bf5eba","tid":1577170,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:45:22.000Z","msg":"冇用架啦，而家拉邊個黑社會都冇用<br />\n起碼拉埋個警司先有啲啲用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:50:39.000Z","msg":"拉晒元朗天水圍黑警就真"},{"pid":"5886c5079e4792f53a204878f8d35d2d7316d6dd","tid":1577170,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"64cff1e976bb4f1ef36c506a8948cc2d335832f2","tid":1577170,"uid":127708,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:46:25.000Z","msg":"救樓主阿媽<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C3k2LRM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC3k2LRM.png&h=ec348c34&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:52:17.000Z","msg":"thx bro"},{"pid":"3dc31f2a849423a21f7d5f850391f695e8db5421","tid":1577170,"uid":148262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:52:30.000Z","msg":"就算拉左佢入狗屋都肯定冇斷手斷腳架啦<br />\n一定唔同對待架"},{"pid":"9cee78c88dac527c467e2828dee29884b28881b8","tid":1577170,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:52:59.000Z","msg":"都就死啦 屌"},{"pid":"98232025843b7115db6c731dee96e84171bdb892","tid":1577170,"uid":43663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:53:43.000Z","msg":"搞到依家私了先拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保護佢地咩"},{"pid":"ccdb2a0ad72287466365b9ed0c33a8600e3b6e15","tid":1577170,"uid":298385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:53:49.000Z","msg":"呢件廢佬都未開波自己訓低，有咩好捉<img src=\"/a